nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A high-quality (300 dpi) chibi-style fantasy illustration in the aspect ratio of a Magic: The Gathering card. The artwork is colorful, detailed, and humorous, with exaggerated proportions and expressive characters. The scene should be dynamic and playful, fitting the whimsical and fun tone of a fantasy trading card game. No text, no borders, just the pure artwork. The artwork should display "A swarm of tiny, goofy creatures in a chaotic brawl, dropping their weapons and tripping over each other."

nodes.title: Chatbox Overlay - Textbox
widgets_values:
As Deadpool enters, you may exchange his text box and another creature's.

At the beginning of your upkeep, you lose 3 life.

, Sacrifice this creature: Each other player draws a card.
